MOTION DOCKET

97-2637. State ex rel. Montgomery v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 96APD12-1749. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Franklin County. Whereas appellant has filed a supplement to the briefs that does not include the proof of service required by S.Ct.Prac.R. XIV(2)(C),

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that appellant’s supplement to the briefs be, and hereby is, stricken.
